<?Baker:ðŸž> **Bakers** <?Baker:ðŸž> 

The Bakers is a trusted townsfolk group containing all the bakers and nobody else. Should a baker turn into a wolf, all the bakers turn into butchers, however if a baker betrays the group in any other way, the other bakers will not know.
Whenever the wolfpack kills a Baker for the first time, they will be able to attack an additional time in the next night.
